// A 2/2 carrying a single intrinsic combat keyword — exercises the
// `Ability::Keyword(KeywordAbility::Trample)` grammar through the real plugin
// loader (macro reader active). Behavior is unimplemented; this only proves
// the keyword parses as a known variant and `has_keyword` can find it.
Normal(
    name: "Keyword probe",
    mana_cost: [Generic(1), Green],
    types: [Creature],
    subtypes: [Bear],
    power: 2,
    toughness: 2,
    abilities: [Keyword(Trample)],
)
